value.0: Fashioned from rough-hewn wood, this simple door swings on ill-fitting hinges.
This is a decent set of armor, made to be worn my humans or half-elves. From the looks of it, it wouldn't fit any other race without cutting or stretching.

The tower shield is a veritable wall of protection, though it can be quite cumbersome to carry on an adventure.

This particular tower shield has been crafted with a special care, making it much easier to wield
